{"word":"ἀλγηδών","slug":"ἀλγηδών","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀλγηδών</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀλγέω'><el>ἀλγέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a sense of pain, pain, suffering</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>of mind, <i>pain, grief</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div>"}]}